## Decisions and Action Items

* **Decisions:**
  * **Protocol Renaming:** The working group agreed to deprecate the expansion of the "EDHOC" acronym (Option 2) and transition to "LAKE protocol" as the primary name, using a clarifying sentence in the terminology sections of all active drafts (Option 3).
  * **Voucher CDDL:** The ELA authors will change the Voucher Response CDDL definition from an array to a map in `draft-ietf-lake-authz`.
  * **PSK Hash Association:** The authors of `draft-ietf-lake-edhoc-psk` will formally bind PSKs to hash functions instead of static cipher suites.

* **Action Items:**
  * **Document Editors:** Update terminology sections in all active drafts to reflect the transition from "EDHOC" to the "LAKE protocol."
  * **Chairs:** Initiate Working Group Last Call for `draft-ietf-lake-authz` (ELA).
  * **Chairs:** Locate a Document Shepherd for `draft-ietf-lake-edhoc-impl-cons` and `draft-ietf-lake-app-profiles`.
  * **Yuxuan / Attestation Authors:** Coordinate with Usama offline to share the attestation implementation links and evaluate the proposed attack vectors.

